parsing

Class MessageParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • parsing.MessageParser

  • public class MessageParser
extends Object
    MessageParser implements the functions for reading and parsing probable XML-strings and files by the Document classes in java. Uses a javax.xml.parsers.DocumentBuilder to build a org.w3c.dom.Document corresponding to the XML-string provided. Uses the DOM/SAX implementation.
    Author:
    anton
